{"tid":347942,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[東京]有冇人去過兩國國技館睇相撲比賽?","createTime":"2017-08-05T09:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T16:33:03.000Z","uid":78773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a00fd9f6b4817497b6c32be72c68b28db03a349","tid":347942,"uid":78773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"之前買左機票9月中去東京玩,<br />\n咁啱原來9月份係東京兩國國技館會搞相撲比賽,<br />\n時間係九月：初日9月10日～千秋楽9月24日<br />\n8月5日, 亦即係今日, 開始網上購票,<br />\n我已經買左二樓既票兩張,<br />\n我想問有冇巴絲曾經去過睇相撲比賽,<br />\n知道當日既流程係如果?<br />\n需唔需要一早到? 正式比賽大約係幾時開始? 附近有咩好野食?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2647e7309f71d38fa4bebcccfe89bdbd49db8929","tid":347942,"uid":78773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ded0426d2d072a8648703a484de3feaa71d165","tid":347942,"uid":78773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e767b89018607056ee1a013cf837f5a2c22bd92a","tid":347942,"uid":78773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370b40f9cc9cdf1918695c35d2707f5f9a3af3bd","tid":347942,"uid":78773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870c91728b5664d697398aa2fc232ae